created grandmas,</i>

553
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,560
<i>it seemed to follow a fixed formula.</i>

554
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,520
<i>Thank you, Grandma.</i>

555
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:34,040
<i>Grandmas' sliced apples</i>

556
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:35,880
<i>always have
the subtle flavor of green onions.</i>

557
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:39,040
{\an8}<i>Grandmas always hunch over,</i>

