{\an8}<i>yet their steps are steady.</i>

559
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,600
<i>Grandmas' bright white aprons</i>

560
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:46,360
<i>are tidy and clean.</i>

561
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,600
<i>Come and have some.</i>

562
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,680
<i>Have some fruit.</i>

563
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,800
<i>Grandmas always think</i>

564
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:53,960
<i>we never have enough to eat.</i>

565
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,520
<i>Here you go.</i>

566
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:56,840
<i>We still have grapes.</i>

567
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,920
<i>Here.</i>

568
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,120
<i>Enjoy yourselves.</i>

569
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:04,000
<i>Grandmas' living spaces are small,</i>

