00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:06,560
<i>too small to fit large furniture.</i>

571
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,760
<i>Yet they are also spacious.</i>

572
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:09,800
<i>They are spacious enough</i>

573
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:11,560
<i>to encompass our entire childhood.</i>

574
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,120
<i>I kind of miss my grandma,</i>

575
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:18,480
<i>but I dare not tell Dad</i>

